rmance review meetings, with attention \ngiven to their frequency and closure. Also, during the Safety committee meeting/Gemba", "metadata": {"source": "/content/drive/MyDrive/pidilite/Annual-Report-2022-2023.pdf", "page": 88}, "type": "Document"}}